{"id":160,"parent_id":158,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":160,"title":"2 Corinthians 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Cor.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","Saints should love and forgive one another—They always triumph in Christ."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.1","order":"03.10.002.18488"},["b","1"],"But I determined this with myself, that I would not come again to you in heaviness."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.2","order":"03.10.002.18489"},["b","2"],"For if I make you sorry, who is he then that maketh me glad, but the same which is made sorry by me?"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.3","order":"03.10.002.18490"},["b","3"],"And I wrote this same unto you, lest, when I came, I should have sorrow from them of whom I ought to rejoice; having",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"confidence"],"in you all, that my joy is",["i","the joy"],"of you all."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.4","order":"03.10.002.18491"},["b","4"],"For out of much affliction and anguish of heart I wrote unto you with many tears; not that ye should be grieved, but that ye might know the love which I have more abundantly unto you."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.5","order":"03.10.002.18492"},["b","5"],"But if any have caused grief, he hath not grieved me, but in part: that I may not overcharge you all."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.6","order":"03.10.002.18493"},["b","6"],"Sufficient to such a man",["i","is"],"this punishment, which",["i","was inflicted"],"of many."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.7","order":"03.10.002.18494"},["b","7"],"So that contrariwise ye",["i","ought"],"rather to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"forgive"],["i","him,"],"and comfort",["i","him,"],"lest perhaps such a one should be swallowed up with overmuch sorrow."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.8","order":"03.10.002.18495"},["b","8"],"Wherefore I beseech you that ye would confirm",["i","your"],"love toward him."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.9","order":"03.10.002.18496"},["b","9"],"For to this end also did I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"write"],", that I might know the proof of you, whether ye be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"obedient"],"in all things."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.10","order":"03.10.002.18497"},["b","10"],"To whom ye forgive any thing, I",["i","forgive"],"also: for if I forgave any thing, to whom I forgave",["i","it,"],"for your sakes",["i","forgave I it"],"in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"person"],"of Christ;"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.11","order":"03.10.002.18498"},["b","11"],"Lest",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"Satan"],"should get an advantage of us: for we are not ignorant of his devices."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.12","order":"03.10.002.18499"},["b","12"],"Furthermore, when I came to Troas to",["i","preach"],"Christ’s gospel, and a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"door"],"was opened unto me of the Lord,"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.13","order":"03.10.002.18500"},["b","13"],"I had no rest in my spirit, because I found not Titus my brother: but taking my leave of them, I went from thence into Macedonia."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.14","order":"03.10.002.18501"},["b","14"],"Now thanks",["i","be"],"unto God, which always causeth us to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"triumph"],"in Christ, and maketh manifest the savour of his knowledge by us in every place."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.15","order":"03.10.002.18502"},["b","15"],"For we are unto God a sweet savour of Christ, in them that are saved, and in them that perish:"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.16","order":"03.10.002.18503"},["b","16"],"To the one",["i","we are"],"the savour of death unto death; and to the other the savour of life unto life. And who",["i","is"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"sufficient"],"for these things?"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.17","order":"03.10.002.18504"},["b","17"],"For we are not as many, which",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"corrupt"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"word"],"of God: but as of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"sincerity"],", but as of God, in the sight of God speak we in Christ."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.3a","order":"03.10.002.18505"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.22"},"2 Cor. 8:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.7a","order":"03.10.002.18507"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/forgive"},"TG Forgive"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.9a","order":"03.10.002.18509"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-writing-of"},"TG Scriptures, Writing of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.9b","order":"03.10.002.18511"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/7.15"},"2 Cor. 7:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.10a","order":"03.10.002.18513"},["b","10a"],["span.small","GR"],"presence."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.11a","order":"03.10.002.18515"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.20.20-22"},"2 Pet. 2:20 (20–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.12a","order":"03.10.002.18517"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/14.27"},"Acts 14:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/16.9"},"1 Cor. 16:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.14a","order":"03.10.002.18519"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/8.37"},"Rom. 8:37"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.16a","order":"03.10.002.18521"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.5.5-6"},"2 Cor. 3:5 (5–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.17a","order":"03.10.002.18523"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.2"},"2 Cor. 4:2"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-the-early-christian-church"},"TG Apostasy of the Early Christian Church"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.17b","order":"03.10.002.18525"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-preservation-of"},"TG Scriptures, Preservation of"],"."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.17c","order":"03.10.002.18527"},["b","17c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sincere"},"TG Sincere"],"."]]}
